title: Sutter County Airport
text: Sutter County Airport is a public <a href="airport">airport</a> located one mile (1.6 km) south of <a href="Yuba%20City%2C%20California">Yuba City</a>, serving <a href="Sutter%20County%2C%20California">Sutter County</a>, <a href="California">California</a>, <a href="United%20States">USA</a>. This <a href="general%20aviation">general aviation</a> airport covers and has one <a href="runway">runway</a>.
